<td>Beginner to Intermediate</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>What you need</strong></td>
<td>A <a href="/best/ai-blog-writing-tools/">keyword research tool</a> (free options work), Google Search, and a text editor or CMS</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
